OWASP ZAP	Build images (parallel)	2026-03-06T09:23:36.4814565Z               "body": "# PR — Epic 22.1: Minigame Contract v2 Foundation\n\n## Summary\n\nIntroduce Minigame Contract v2 type system with interaction metadata (interactionType, requiredInputs, timerPolicy, layoutClass, uniqueDifficultyKnobs) and annotate all 6 enabled minigames. Add validation utilities and unit tests.\n\n## Tasks\n\n- [ ] T1: Define Contract v2 types and enums\n- [ ] T2: Annotate all 6 minigames with v2 metadata in registry\n- [ ] T3: Add contract validation utility and unit tests\n- [ ] T4: Update MinigameRenderer and serving to pass v2 metadata\n- [ ] T5: E2E smoke assertion for play route\n",
